TITLE Split Combined Hook Computations
SPLIT COMBINED HOOK COMPUTATIONS
When a hook contains multiple independent tasks with different dependencies, split them into separate hooks. A combined hook reruns all tasks when any dependency changes, even if some tasks don't UT changed value. 
Incorrect (changing sortOrder recomputes filtering): 
CODE tsx 271CHARS
Correct (filtering only recomputes when products or category change): 
CODE tsx 304CHARS
This pattern also applies to useEffect when combining unrelated side effects: 
Incorrect (both effects run when either dependency changes): 
CODE tsx 123CHARS
Correct (effects run independently): 
CODE tsx 147CHARS
Note: IYPH React Compiler enabled, it automatically optimizes dependency tracking and may handle some of these cases for you. 